sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as 用户
  participant Mobile as 移动端 Expo App
  participant Api as NestJS AiController
  participant AiService as AiService
  participant Prompt as PromptRegistry
  participant Guard as RateLimiter / CircuitBreaker
  participant Provider as OpenAiAdapter
  participant Local as 本地 AI 服务
  participant GLM as 智谱 GLM 降级
  participant Validator as OutputValidator
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  User->>Mobile: 输入目标 / 愿景 / 局部辅助上下文
  Mobile->>Api: POST /ai/generations 或 /ai/assist
  Api->>AiService: generateDraft(userId, scenario, input)
  AiService->>Guard: 检查限流与熔断
  AiService->>Prompt: 读取场景模板并 build prompt
  AiService->>Provider: generate(prompt, model, timeout)
  Provider->>Local: POST /chat/completions
  alt 本地服务成功
    Local-->>Provider: JSON 字符串内容
  else 本地服务失败且配置了 fallback key
    Provider->>GLM: POST /chat/completions
    GLM-->>Provider: JSON 字符串内容
  else 双 provider 失败
    Provider-->>AiService: 抛错
    AiService->>Guard: 记录失败
    AiService-->>Api: 错误响应
    Api-->>Mobile: HTTP error
  end
  Provider-->>AiService: rawOutput
  AiService->>AiService: JSON.parse(rawOutput)
  AiService->>Validator: 按 scenario 做 Zod 校验
  Validator-->>AiService: outputJson
  AiService->>DB: 创建 AiGeneration(status=COMPLETED)
  AiService->>Guard: 记录成功
  AiService-->>Api: GenerationDto
  Api-->>Mobile: 草案 id + outputJson
  User->>Mobile: 修改并确认草案
  Mobile->>Api: POST /ai/generations/:id/confirm
  Api->>AiService: confirmGeneration(userId, id, target, edits)
  AiService->>DB: 事务落库业务对象并更新 status=CONFIRMED
  DB-->>AiService: applied counts + generation
  AiService-->>Api: ConfirmGenerationResponse
  Api-->>Mobile: 确认结果
